flowchart TD
    Plan[AI/DSL workflow plan] --> Canon[Canonicalize node types<br/>registry aliases resolved]
    Canon --> Build[Build nodes + edges]
    Build --> Ports[Validate ports and handles]
    Ports --> DAG[Validate DAG<br/>no cycles, no broken links]
    DAG --> Branch[Branch/merge reconciliation<br/>if, switch, try/catch]
    Branch --> Repair[Deterministic graph repairs<br/>missing links, invalid shapes]
    Repair --> Ready{Executable graph?}
    Ready -->|yes| Persist[Persist graph state<br/>AWS RDB/RDS]
    Ready -->|no| Block[Return diagnostics<br/>do not execute]
